I saw Yuzaki coming out from behind the hospital

1097
01:15:38,334 --> 01:15:40,935
Oh, I didn't see him

1098
01:15:40,960 --> 01:15:42,803
Don't worry.
You saw him

1099
01:15:44,912 --> 01:15:47,982
I see, so you'll give me 30,000yen

1100
01:15:52,053 --> 01:15:53,982
Then read aloud what you have written so far

1101
01:15:55,982 --> 01:16:00,599
I'm sorry to write you a letter suddenly.
Do you remember me?

1102
01:16:01,318 --> 01:16:04,256
I'm Emiko Toyama, a nurse who worked with her at the hospital

1103
01:16:04,639 --> 01:16:08,529
Do you know why I am writing to you?

1104
01:16:09,209 --> 01:16:14,404
I saw you come out of the back of the hospital at the time she was killed

1105
01:16:15,756 --> 01:16:18,146
I've been silent about that until now

1106
01:16:18,701 --> 01:16:20,092
How do you write it?

1107
01:16:21,060 --> 01:16:21,928
write whatever you like

1108
01:16:23,678 --> 01:16:24,896
I've been silent about that until now

1109
01:16:26,115 --> 01:16:27,342
Because I hated her and

1110
01:16:28,029 --> 01:16:33,732
Because I thought it didn't matter to me who killed her

1111
01:16:34,607 --> 01:16:35,873
It's hot

1112
01:16:36,224 --> 01:16:37,748
Put the fan on me.

1113
01:16:38,326 --> 01:16:40,334
However, due to some recent circumstances

1114
01:16:40,359 --> 01:16:41,881
Speak more slowly

1115
01:16:42,482 --> 01:16:44,795
However,recently

1116
01:16:45,904 --> 01:16:48,505
I suddenly needed money for some reason

1117
01:16:51,849 --> 01:16:55,545
Please prepare 1 million yen by 12:00 tomorrow

1118
01:16:55,896 --> 01:16:56,771
1 million yen?

1119
01:16:58,553 --> 01:16:59,607
Please bring it

1120
01:17:21,951 --> 01:17:24,881
Yuzaki has not left yet?

1121
01:17:25,224 --> 01:17:27,107
He is on the meeting

1122
01:17:28,271 --> 01:17:30,771
Then he has a sales meeting

1123
01:17:31,412 --> 01:17:32,490
He's been in the office for a while

1124
01:17:33,342 --> 01:17:35,553
I see.
Thank you

1125
01:17:59,482 --> 01:18:01,834
Make sure you come.
Don't bring the money

1126
01:18:01,889 --> 01:18:03,185
Yes. to Myogadani

1127
01:18:14,896 --> 01:18:17,982
This is for you as we promised

1128
01:18:20,537 --> 01:18:21,279
Thanks

1129
01:18:22,795 --> 01:18:24,411
I'm sorry for the unreasonable request.

1130
01:18:25,568 --> 01:18:27,295
what do you use this money for ?

1131
01:18:28,224 --> 01:18:29,021
I'll find out soon

1132
01:18:29,849 --> 01:18:32,295
I will reveal his true identity

1133
01:18:32,857 --> 01:18:34,045
So I need this money

1134
01:18:35,326 --> 01:18:39,178
You're going to catch the criminal yourself

1135
01:18:41,162 --> 01:18:42,467
You want to take a revenge?

1136
01:18:43,842 --> 01:18:44,834
Of course

1137
01:18:45,842 --> 01:18:47,568
He ruined my life

1138
01:18:48,631 --> 01:18:49,803
He is the culprit for sure

1139
01:18:50,467 --> 01:18:54,514
You're the one who knows I had nothing to do with this.

1140
01:18:55,232 --> 01:18:56,381
You're the one who knows

1141
01:18:57,935 --> 01:18:59,990
Yes I know

1142
01:19:01,592 --> 01:19:03,756
But I couldn't say anything

1143
01:19:05,014 --> 01:19:05,951
Not only me

1144
01:19:07,115 --> 01:19:08,006
You too

1145
01:19:08,576 --> 01:19:10,373
You were afraid if Kazumi knows

1146
01:19:11,420 --> 01:19:13,428
You were afraid to get rid of the company

1147
01:19:14,256 --> 01:19:17,537
But in the end nothing remained

1148
01:19:21,568 --> 01:19:24,920
When I first met you, you were so nice.

1149
01:19:25,553 --> 01:19:26,701
You were very hopeful

1150
01:19:27,678 --> 01:19:30,053
I felt so fresh.

1151
01:19:31,865 --> 01:19:36,553
I was thinking of going on a new life with you

1152
01:19:38,092 --> 01:19:41,818
I thought life with Kasumi was very miserable

1153
01:19:43,896 --> 01:19:46,092
But in the end it didn't work

1154
01:19:48,193 --> 01:19:50,959
You couldn't forget about the company after all.

1155
01:19:52,279 --> 01:19:54,303
Position, promotion

1156
01:19:55,084 --> 01:19:56,459
That's all you needed

1157
01:19:57,490 --> 01:19:57,881
Hisako

1158
01:19:57,920 --> 01:19:59,951
Don't say anything

1159
01:20:02,662 --> 01:20:04,232
You didn't choose me

1160
01:20:05,623 --> 01:20:08,545
So I couldn't leave from Kasumi

1161
01:20:12,982 --> 01:20:16,920
You couldn't understand my feelings

1162
01:20:38,006 --> 01:20:38,701
Thanks

1163
01:20:41,482 --> 01:20:43,248
I wanted more

1164
01:20:45,271 --> 01:20:46,615
578-3521

1165
01:20:47,974 --> 01:20:52,092
If Yuzaki brought me 1 million yen, how much would you give me?

1166
01:20:53,029 --> 01:20:54,021
I'll give you all

1167
01:20:54,998 --> 01:20:55,904
I'm glad

1168
01:21:08,279 --> 01:21:11,006
Hello? are you yuzaki residence?

1169
01:21:11,428 --> 01:21:13,685
Can I talk to Mr.Yuzaki?

1170
01:21:15,045 --> 01:21:16,935
Hi, it's me

1171
01:21:18,099 --> 01:21:20,084
Oh you don't remember?

1172
01:21:20,943 --> 01:21:22,764
I'm Toyama who wrote a letter to you

1173
01:21:23,803 --> 01:21:25,303
What about my request?

1174
01:21:26,576 --> 01:21:28,076
I saw you for sure

1175
01:21:29,318 --> 01:21:30,818
Call me when you make a decision

1176
01:21:31,514 --> 01:21:33,170
I'll wait by 6 am tomorrow

1177
01:21:34,029 --> 01:21:36,498
I'll go to police if you don't come

1178
01:21:37,537 --> 01:21:41,959
Here is my number 851-2751

1179
01:21:44,107 --> 01:21:44,584
See you then

1180
01:21:47,115 --> 01:21:49,803
See?
It worth 30,000yen

1181
01:21:50,881 --> 01:21:54,209
Hello?
Connect here if someone call for Toyama

1182
01:21:55,599 --> 01:21:56,420
Hey

1183
01:22:34,326 --> 01:22:35,849
There is a calling

1184
01:22:38,670 --> 01:22:41,178
Oh sorry. I called wrong number

1185
01:22:51,724 --> 01:22:52,654
Are you going home?

1186
01:22:53,014 --> 01:22:54,631
Because It's already past 6 o'clock

1187
01:22:54,656 --> 01:22:55,662
Please wait a little more

1188
01:22:57,060 --> 01:22:57,295
OK?

1189
01:22:57,373 --> 01:22:58,092
No

1190
01:22:58,982 --> 01:23:02,560
We don't get a call from him anymore

1191
01:23:03,271 --> 01:23:05,131
It takes time to go home

1192
01:23:05,357 --> 01:23:06,076
Please wait a little more

1193
01:23:06,771 --> 01:23:09,084
We promised that

1194
01:23:10,928 --> 01:23:12,107
Thanks for 30,000yen

1195
01:23:56,670 --> 01:23:58,732
No! Get off of me.

1196
01:23:59,279 --> 01:24:00,279
Get off of me.

1197
01:24:00,982 --> 01:24:02,102
Get off of me.

1198
01:24:13,115 --> 01:24:13,787
Wait!

1199
01:24:17,013 --> 01:24:19,076
We are arresting you for murder.

1200
01:24:22,787 --> 01:24:23,912
Stay down!

1201
01:24:25,006 --> 01:24:25,912
Get off of me

1202
01:24:25,982 --> 01:24:27,022
Get off of me

1203
01:24:28,678 --> 01:24:29,615
What the hell?

1204
01:24:30,310 --> 01:24:31,553
Come to police

1205
01:24:43,342 --> 01:24:47,482
It doesn't matter to you whether he's the culprit or not

1206
01:24:48,310 --> 01:24:52,912
That's bullshit. listen,
Yuzaki tried to fire me

1207
01:24:53,318 --> 01:24:55,615
He was arrested for murder

1208
01:24:56,006 --> 01:25:00,037
And Chief Miyama has also been arrested as an embezzlement of 3 million yen.

1209
01:25:00,389 --> 01:25:02,381
I have nothing to do with the incident

1210
01:25:02,920 --> 01:25:04,420
I am innocent

1211
01:25:04,889 --> 01:25:07,857
So the company needs to reconsider my resignation.

1212
01:25:08,514 --> 01:25:12,279
You have been deemed unfit to be our employee.

1213
01:25:12,998 --> 01:25:15,053
It's needless to talk with you

1214
01:25:15,560 --> 01:25:17,373
I speak directly with Managing Director Domoto

1215
01:25:18,021 --> 01:25:18,810
Wait

1216
01:25:21,326 --> 01:25:24,678
It's waste to go.
Your return to the company was denied at the meeting.

1217
01:25:25,107 --> 01:25:27,607
What? at the meeting?

1218
01:25:28,248 --> 01:25:30,349
An urgent meeting was held last night

1219
01:25:31,459 --> 01:25:33,545
Your disposition also became an issue at the meeting

1220
01:25:34,740 --> 01:25:37,951
Our company does not allow your reinstatement to protect the authority of the company

1221
01:25:38,724 --> 01:25:39,920
So decided

1222
01:25:40,592 --> 01:25:43,342
This is what we have to do.

1223
01:25:43,982 --> 01:25:46,014
They don't have time to care about you

1224
01:25:47,685 --> 01:25:50,107
There is a call for you,chief

1225
01:25:52,631 --> 01:25:57,576
I'm the section chief now, instead of you.

1226
01:25:59,099 --> 01:26:00,170
Hello? I'm Furuya

1227
01:26:02,084 --> 01:26:05,779
It's challenging to get the job back up and running again.

1228
01:26:06,873 --> 01:26:08,146
Thanks in advance

1229
01:26:11,529 --> 01:26:13,373
We will contact you about that material within a few days.

1230
01:26:18,553 --> 01:26:19,529
You've had a terrible time.

1231
01:26:20,451 --> 01:26:21,553
You were unlucky

1232
01:26:31,959 --> 01:26:32,670
Fuji-san

1233
01:26:34,904 --> 01:26:36,982
It seems that Chief Miyama was arrested.

1234
01:26:37,576 --> 01:26:39,662
Our editor-in-chief wants to see you

1235
01:26:40,467 --> 01:26:43,764
He wants to know because you know the inside story of the case

1236
01:26:44,271 --> 01:26:46,560
The department chief is a murderer and the section chief is an embezzlement

1237
01:26:47,178 --> 01:26:48,420
This is interesting

1238
01:26:48,748 --> 01:26:52,107
You may be entitled to compensation from the company.

1239
01:26:53,139 --> 01:26:55,920
Please don't make such an unpleasant face

1240
01:26:56,732 --> 01:27:00,459
You are already banished from the company

1241
01:27:02,092 --> 01:27:05,396
It's all over.
This is our number

1242
01:27:06,295 --> 01:27:08,178
Our editor chief is waiting for you

1243
01:28:22,045 --> 01:28:23,435
I've left from Kasumi

1244
01:28:24,115 --> 01:28:24,514
Eh?

1245
01:28:27,053 --> 01:28:31,303
I suffered a lot trying to forget you

1246
01:28:33,201 --> 01:28:34,592
But I couldn't

1247
01:28:36,482 --> 01:28:39,006
Let's get together

1248
01:28:44,404 --> 01:28:45,959
I have nothing for me anymore

1249
01:28:47,982 --> 01:28:49,881
The company didn't protect me either

1250
01:28:52,646 --> 01:28:53,646
Is that ok for you

1251
01:28:56,138 --> 01:28:56,739
Sure

1252
01:28:59,459 --> 01:29:00,803
I'll follow you

